name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Swamp
info.flavor_text: You expected to meet hostile drow in this ancient ruin . . . but they fled long ago. What darkness could have driven them out?

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Plains
info.flavor_text: Venturing beneath the desert sands, you've discovered an alien power pulsing with inconceivable energy.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Island
info.flavor_text: In crystal-studded waters far below the surface, you've discovered an incubating egg of mysterious origin.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Evolving Wilds
info.oracle_text: {T}, Sacrifice Evolving Wilds: Search your library for a basic land card, put it onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.
info.flavor_text: Parts of Faerûn still churn with the magic of arrogant Netherese archmages long dead.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Dungeon Map
info.oracle_text:
{T}: Add {C}.
{3}, {T}: Venture into the dungeon. Activate only as a sorcery. (Enter the first room or advance to the next room.)
info.flavor_text: "Wait, is that a secret door? I can't tell for sure . . . there's some blood in the way."

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Hama Pashar, Ruin Seeker
info.oracle_text: Room abilities of dungeons you own trigger an additional time.
info.flavor_text: "Someone took the time to carve these inscriptions. The least we can do is care enough to read them."

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Minimus Containment
info.oracle_text:
Enchant nonland permanent
Enchanted permanent is a Treasure artifact with "{T}, Sacrifice this artifact: Add one mana of any color," and it loses all other abilities. (If it was a creature, it's no longer a creature.)

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Bucknard's Everfull Purse
info.oracle_text: {1}, {T}: Roll a d4 and create a number of Treasure tokens equal to the result. The player to your right gains control of Bucknard's Everfull Purse.
info.flavor_text: As long as it's never left empty, this magic pouch produces coins every dawn.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Clay Golem
info.oracle_text:
{6}, Roll a d8: Monstrosity X, where X is the result. (If this creature isn't monstrous, put X +1/+1 counters on it and it becomes monstrous.)
Berserk — When Clay Golem becomes monstrous, destroy target permanent.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Thorough Investigation
info.oracle_text:
Whenever you attack, investigate. (Create a Clue token. It's an artifact with "{2}, Sacrifice this artifact: Draw a card.")
Whenever you sacrifice a Clue, venture into the dungeon. (Enter the first room or advance to the next room.)

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Minn, Wily Illusionist
info.oracle_text:
Whenever you draw your second card each turn, create a 1/1 blue Illusion creature token with "This creature gets +1/+0 for each other Illusion you control."
Whenever an Illusion you control dies, you may put a permanent card with mana value less than or equal to that creature's power from your hand onto the battlefield.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Midnight Pathlighter
info.oracle_text:
Creatures you control can't be blocked except by legendary creatures.
Whenever one or more creatures you control deal combat damage to a player, venture into the dungeon. (Enter the first room or advance to the next room.)

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Radiant Solar
info.oracle_text:
Flying, lifelink
Whenever Radiant Solar or another nontoken creature you control enters, venture into the dungeon. (Enter the first room or advance to the next room.)
{W}, Discard Radiant Solar: Venture into the dungeon and you gain 3 life.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Rod of Absorption
info.oracle_text:
Whenever a player casts an instant or sorcery spell, exile it instead of putting it into a graveyard as it resolves.
{X}, {T}, Sacrifice Rod of Absorption: You may cast any number of spells from among cards exiled with Rod of Absorption with total mana value X or less without paying their mana costs.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Revivify
info.oracle_text:
Roll a d20 and add the number of creature cards in your graveyard that were put there from the battlefield this turn.
1—14 | Return all creature cards in your graveyard that were put there from the battlefield this turn to your hand.
15+ | Return those cards from your graveyard to the battlefield.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Immovable Rod
info.oracle_text:
You may choose not to untap Immovable Rod during your untap step.
Whenever Immovable Rod becomes untapped, venture into the dungeon.
{3}{W}, {T}: For as long as Immovable Rod remains tapped, another target permanent loses all abilities and can't attack or block.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Phantom Steed
info.oracle_text:
Flash
When Phantom Steed enters, exile another target creature you control until Phantom Steed leaves the battlefield.
Whenever Phantom Steed attacks, create a tapped and attacking token that's a copy of the exiled card, except it's an Illusion in addition to its other types. Sacrifice that token at end of combat.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Component Pouch
info.oracle_text:
{T}, Remove a component counter from Component Pouch: Add two mana of different colors.
{T}: Roll a d20.
1—9 | Put a component counter on Component Pouch.
10—20 | Put two component counters on Component Pouch.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Extract Brain
info.oracle_text: Target opponent chooses X cards from their hand. Look at those cards. You may cast a spell from among them without paying its mana cost.
info.flavor_text: No thought is as succulent as a secret.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Grave Endeavor
info.oracle_text: Roll two d10 and choose one result. Return a creature card from your graveyard to the battlefield with a number of +1/+1 counters on it equal to that result. Then each opponent loses X life and you gain X life, where X is the other result.
info.flavor_text: Not alive, not dead, but definitely furious.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Wand of Orcus

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Arcane Endeavor
info.oracle_text: Roll two d8 and choose one result. Draw cards equal to that result. Then you may cast an instant or sorcery spell with mana value less than or equal to the other result from your hand without paying its mana cost.
info.flavor_text: Late at night, when dreams touch a studious mind, bouts of inspiration strike.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Sol Ring
info.oracle_text: {T}: Add {C}{C}.
info.flavor_text: Lost to time is the artificer's art of trapping light from a distant star in a ring of purest gold.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Arcane Sanctum
info.oracle_text:
Arcane Sanctum enters tapped.
{T}: Add {W}, {U}, or {B}.
info.flavor_text:
"We must rely on our own knowledge, not on the dogma of the seekers or the mutterings of the sphinxes."
—Tullus of Palandius

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Ashen Rider
info.oracle_text:
Flying
When Ashen Rider enters or dies, exile target permanent.
info.flavor_text: One offering to appease her on her arrival. Another to celebrate her departure.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Azorius Chancery
info.oracle_text:
Azorius Chancery enters tapped.
When Azorius Chancery enters, return a land you control to its owner's hand.
{T}: Add {W}{U}.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Baleful Strix
info.oracle_text:
Flying, deathtouch
When Baleful Strix enters, draw a card.
info.flavor_text: Its beak rends flesh and bone, exposing the tender marrow of dream.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Arcane Signet
info.oracle_text: {T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander's color identity.
info.flavor_text: It started as a mere drop of water. The Magic Mirror crystallized it into much more.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Burnished Hart
info.oracle_text: {3}, Sacrifice Burnished Hart: Search your library for up to two basic land cards, put them onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.
info.flavor_text: Forged by divine hands to wander mortal realms.

info.name: Cataclysmic Gearhulk
info.oracle_text:
Vigilance
When Cataclysmic Gearhulk enters, each player chooses an artifact, a creature, an enchantment, and a planeswalker from among the nonland permanents they control, then sacrifices the rest.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Champion of Wits
info.oracle_text:
When Champion of Wits enters, you may draw cards equal to its power. If you do, discard two cards.
Eternalize {5}{U}{U} ({5}{U}{U}, Exile this card from your graveyard: Create a token that's a copy of it, except it's a 4/4 black Zombie Snake Wizard with no mana cost. Eternalize only as a sorcery.)

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Choked Estuary
info.oracle_text:
As Choked Estuary enters, you may reveal an Island or Swamp card from your hand. If you don't, Choked Estuary enters tapped.
{T}: Add {U} or {B}.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Cloudblazer
info.oracle_text:
Flying
When Cloudblazer enters, you gain 2 life and draw two cards.
info.flavor_text: All the aether charts in the world can't compete with the trained eye of a talented scout.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Commander's Sphere
info.oracle_text:
{T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander's color identity.
Sacrifice Commander's Sphere: Draw a card.
info.flavor_text: "The heavens augur weal . . . for me. Woe for you."

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Curator of Mysteries
info.oracle_text:
Flying
Whenever you cycle or discard another card, scry 1.
Cycling {U} ({U}, Discard this card: Draw a card.)
info.flavor_text: To consult a sphinx is a test in patience. Perhaps that's the point.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Command Tower
info.oracle_text: {T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander's color identity.
info.flavor_text:
"Approach my tower on bended knee or depart from it as ash upon the wind."
—Gadwick, the Wizened

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Darkwater Catacombs
info.flavor_text: Underdark flooding has swallowed ancient drow burial chambers, which are now haunted . . . and infested with oozes.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Despark
info.oracle_text: Exile target permanent with mana value 4 or greater.
info.flavor_text: Liliana whispered to whatever consciousness Oketra and Bontu had left. "You are the gods. He is the usurper. You know what to do."

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Dimir Aqueduct
info.oracle_text:
Dimir Aqueduct enters tapped.
When Dimir Aqueduct enters, return a land you control to its owner's hand.
{T}: Add {U}{B}.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Doomed Necromancer
info.oracle_text: {B}, {T}, Sacrifice Doomed Necromancer: Return target creature card from your graveyard to the battlefield.
info.flavor_text: Many necromancers share the same last words—the ones that conclude the undeath ritual.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Esper Panorama
info.oracle_text:
{T}: Add {C}.
{1}, {T}, Sacrifice Esper Panorama: Search your library for a basic Plains, Island, or Swamp card, put it onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.
info.flavor_text: Esper is an expansive canvas painted by precise, controlling hands.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Eternal Dragon
info.oracle_text:
Flying
{3}{W}{W}: Return Eternal Dragon from your graveyard to your hand. Activate only during your upkeep.
Plainscycling {2} ({2}, Discard this card: Search your library for a Plains card, reveal it, put it into your hand, then shuffle.)

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Exotic Orchard
info.oracle_text: {T}: Add one mana of any color that a land an opponent controls could produce.
info.flavor_text:
"It was a strange morning. When we awoke, we found our trees transformed. We didn't know whether to water them or polish them."
—Pulan, Bant orchardist

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Fellwar Stone
info.oracle_text: {T}: Add one mana of any color that a land an opponent controls could produce.
info.flavor_text:

—Mairsil, the Pretender

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Forbidden Alchemy

Look at the top four cards of your library. Put one of them into your hand and the rest into your graveyard.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Geier Reach Sanitarium
info.oracle_text:
{T}: Add {C}.
{2}, {T}: Each player draws a card, then discards a card.
info.flavor_text: All are welcome.

info.oracle_text:
{T}: Add {C}.
{T}, Sacrifice a creature: You gain 1 life.

info.name: Karmic Guide

Flying, protection from black
Echo {3}{W}{W} (At the beginning of your upkeep, if this came under your control since the beginning of your last upkeep, sacrifice it unless you pay its echo cost.)

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Lightning Greaves
info.oracle_text:
Equipped creature has haste and shroud. (It can't be the target of spells or abilities.)
Equip {0}
info.flavor_text: After lightning struck the cliffs, the ore became iron, the iron became steel, and the steel became greaves. The lightning never left.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)

info.oracle_text:
Flying

Evoke {2}{U} (You may cast this spell for its evoke cost. If you do, it's sacrificed when it enters.)

info.name: Murder of Crows
info.oracle_text:
Flying
Whenever another creature dies, you may draw a card. If you do, discard a card.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)

info.flavor_text: It shambled from the cloud of ash and bone dust, undeterred by its own extinction.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Necrotic Sliver
info.oracle_text: All Slivers have "{3}, Sacrifice this permanent: Destroy target permanent."

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)
info.name: Nimbus Maze

{T}: Add {C}.
{T}: Add {W}. Activate only if you control an Island.
{T}: Add {U}. Activate only if you control a Plains.
info.flavor_text: To find its center is to find one's own.

name: Dungeons of Death (Adventures in the Forgotten Realms Commander Precon Decklist)

{T}: Draw a card, then discard a card.
{2}{U}{B}, {T}, Sacrifice Obsessive Stitcher: Return target creature card from your graveyard to the battlefield.
